## Keyword filter

The Keyword filter performs a text search in the field(s) you choose

## Options

- Label
- Placeholder
- Key
- Look for matches in:

Pick the fields where this filter perform a search in. Note: After making changes to the fields you must manually reindex for changes to take effect.
- Icon

## Display modes

This filter has two display modes when added to your [search form](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_search-form-vx-widget_.md)
